            <h1>API</h1>
            <h2>The API can be used to upload &amp; download data.</h2>
            <p>Uploads can be sent anonymously, however downloading data requires an account. We do recommend creating an account even if you're just uploading data, although optional, it's useful to check the status of your upload.</p>
